metadata.title: Spring Bald Eagle Population Surveys

creators.name: Wildlife Service (USFWS), Oil Spill Administration Office

metadata.description: Data Type: Birds;  This theme consists of survey design coverages for bald eagle population studies, including random plots and coastal surveys by island group. Scale is 1:63,360.
